About this property

Comfortable Accommodations: Grand Opera Hotel in Kutaisi offers family rooms with air-conditioning, private bathrooms, and city views. Each room includes a work desk, mini-bar, and free WiFi. Exceptional Facilities: Guests enjoy free WiFi, private check-in and check-out, a 24-hour front desk, and a concierge service. Additional amenities include a coffee shop, room service, and a paid shuttle. Prime Location: Located 12 mi from Kutaisi International Airport, the hotel is near Colchis Fountain (5-minute walk), White Bridge (984 feet), and Bagrati Cathedral (less than 0.6 mi). An ice-skating rink is also nearby. Guest Satisfaction: Highly rated for its convenient location, attentive staff, and delicious breakfast.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.6 for a two-person trip.
